title: [Celasian's General Store]
[Celasian's Outfitting]
description: Beneath a high arched ceiling, a gold and crimson wyvern tapestry hangs on one of the textured red silk walls.  A iron-bound ebonwood chest and an intricately carved ebonwood stand sit in opposite corners while a serene golden wyvern fountain rests on a parquet red maple floor.
